## Key Technical Facts

- **Lighthouse cannot be re-delegated.** Proxy access
  cannot pass through to us. End client tenant admin
  must delegate directly to our tenant.
- **Lighthouse alone cannot deploy data connectors**
  in a managed workspace. Existing workspace means
  connectors already exist. Client-side hands needed
  only for changes or fixes.
- **Sentinel Azure portal retirement: March 31, 2027**
  (extended from July 2026). Lighthouse remains the
  supported MSSP pattern. Defender portal process
  is on our roadmap — not a blocker for this onboarding.
- **Post-July-2025 workspaces** may be auto-onboarded
  to the Defender portal. Confirm which portal the
  end client team uses day-to-day.
- **Stage before production.** Triage pipeline runs
  in stage first. Validate everything before
  promoting to production.

